The '''crystal impling jar''' is the result of successfully catching a [[crystal impling]], while also having an empty [[impling jar]]. Level 80 [[Hunter]] is required to catch them.

==Loot==
At current [[Grand Exchange]] prices, opening a crystal impling jar gives {{Coins|{{ImpValue|crystal|jar=yes}} round 0}} worth of loot on average. If you include growing the [[Crystal acorn]]s , you can use [[Crystal shard]]s to create [[Divine potion]]s, this increases the value to {{Coins|floor({{#var:LootWithShards}})}}.

{{DropLogProject|jagex=yes}}
===Impling jar===
An empty impling jar is returned when removing the loot, with a 10% chance of it breaking.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1059259735675932672|date=4 November 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.vn/rpWRS|archivedate=23 July 2019|quote=[What are the chances of an impling jar breaking when opening it?] 10% flat rate, I think.}}
